Package bto.Model

Class Enquiry

  • java.lang.Object
    • bto.Model.Enquiry
  • public class Enquiry
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an enquiry submitted by an applicant for a specific project. An enquiry can be replied to by an officer.

        Constructs an Enquiry with the specified details.
        Parameters:
        id - The ID of the enquiry.
        applicantNric - The NRIC of the applicant who submitted the enquiry.
        projectName - The name of the project the enquiry is about.
        enquiryDetails - The details of the enquiry.
        createdTime - The time the enquiry was created.
        reply - The reply to the enquiry (if any).
        repliedBy - The name of the officer who replied to the enquiry (if any).
        repliedTime - The time the enquiry was replied to (if any).
